data.description: Newer home on Eau Claire Southside, near Lowe's creek area. Quiet neighborhood. Perfect home for main level living and expansive living area on the lower level also. 3 bedrooms on main floor, with 4th additional non-conforming bedroom. Two full bath. Family room and tons or additional room for expansion. Poured concrete foundation. Main level laundry, vaulted ceilings, oversized windows, concrete patio in back, covered front porch. Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring and maintenance free siding, windows and home. Insulated, two car garage. Plenty of room for workshop in the garage. Oversized lot.Abutts golf course. Near Fairfax Park. 4th bedroom is non conforming.
